=|author=|date=2020-07-01|last=|format=|work=自由時報電子報|publisher=|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730110804/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3214831|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 意思 ==
「我哋真係好撚鍾意香港」，字面上的意思是「我們真的超級喜歡香港」，當中「[[撚|撚]]」是[[粵語粗口|粵語粗口]]，蘊含着「超級」、「極致」之意，表達了香港人的豪氣；亦蘊含着自嘲的意味，表達了即管香港「樓價高、地價貴、工作慘」，也要堅持留在香港這個地方；更蘊含着香港人的強橫和驕傲，表達對拯救這個地方的渴望和對未來未知的恐懼<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E6%92%9A%E9%90%98%E6%84%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%80%8B-%E6%92%9A-%E5%AD%97/ | title=「我哋真係好撚鐘意香港」個「撚」字 | author=殷琦 | date=2020-07-03 | publisher=立場新聞 | accessdate=2020-07-30 | archive-date=2020-07-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730110811/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E6%92%9A%E9%90%98%E6%84%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%80%8B-%E6%92%9A-%E5%AD%97/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，不會就[[中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法|港區國安法]]被恐懼支配，也不會讓香港淪為另一個[[上海|上海]]、[[北京|北京]]。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=七情上面：貓神學化悲憤為耐力|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%89%af%e5%88%8a/article/20200712/s00005/1594491258341/%e4%b8%83%e6%83%85%e4%b8%8a%e9%9d%a2-%e8%b2%93%e7%a5%9e%e5%ad%b8%e5%8c%96%e6%82%b2%e6%86%a4%e7%82%ba%e8%80%90%e5%8a%9b|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-07-12|format=|work=明報新聞網|publisher=|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204173900/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A/article/20200712/s00005/1594491258341/%E4%B8%83%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2-%E8%B2%93%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%B8%E5%8C%96%E6%82%B2%E6%86%A4%E7%82%BA%E8%80%90%E5%8A%9B|dead-url=no}}</ref>

